    nvl clear


translate English day6_hk_7b776be6:


    nar "The workplace this time around is much noisier compared to earlier this morning. {w}Come to think of it, it's about time for everyone to meet up."


translate English day6_hk_b62c955b:


    nar "I usually stopped by when it was quiet, so it was easy for me to forget this place was usually bustling with activity most of the time."


translate English day6_hk_b59b5796:


    nar "I don't want to bother anyone, but also there's nowhere else I really need to be."


translate English day6_hk_1474defd:


    nar "And besides, the crowd will dissipate before long. {w}After giving it some thought, I wander into a less populated warehouse."


translate English day6_hk_65b85cb7:


    nar "The Cleanup Department clears out the warehouse twice a day--during lunch and right around quitting time. {w}So I'm confident I won't be bothered."


translate English day6_hk_3868121b:


    nar "Despite my deep-seated anxiety, I'm quickly able to find a couple matches and the candle in the exact same place it was yesterday, which calms me down."


translate English day6_hk_27d7bfd7:


    nar "The candle, made of cheap wax, quickly begins to melt down with a crackling sound as soon as the wick catches fire. {w}The flicker of the orange flame paints the darkness with light."


translate English day6_hk_59df0b75:


    nar "I wonder if Maya made it back safely? {w}Just as I begin to lose myself in thought, I'm startled by the loud clang of machinery."


translate English day6_hk_c2765d26:


    nar "Despite finding a place where I can be alone, it's still impossible to relax."


translate English day6_hk_40ea6a45:


    nar "Our main job here in the workplace is dealing with corpses."


translate English day6_hk_f922bf37:


    nar "Friends, family, and even acquaintances sometimes hold proper funerals when confronted with a dead body, but not often."


translate English day6_hk_4c0ae009:


    nar "When the souls then lose their way, their discard husks left to be disposed of by us, the Disposal team. {w}The dregs of their former life are burnt and then buried..."


translate English day6_hk_385392b2:


    nar "I'm still not used to seeing old, rotting bodies being mercilessly ground up into dust. {w}Being turned into an unrecognizable form far removed from their former humanity."


translate English day6_hk_06b1fab3:


    nar "I feel the same watching their bodies burn up in the furnace. {w}Though watching the flames is an adequate distraction."


translate English day6_hk_eee22d27:


    nar "My problem lies more with the smoke. The musky, rotten stench that billows out of the furnace with each burnt corpse. {w}Somehow, the priests on the Disposal Team are able to work while breathing that in."


translate English day6_hk_085f8c99:


    nar "Sweat drips down my forehead as I watch the flames dance in the suffocating air of the warehouse. {w}And at the same time, exhaustion sweeps over me."


translate English day6_hk_6aba397b:


    nar "I should really go outside and clear my mind with some fresh air, but I can do nothing but close my leaden eyelids and take a deep breath."


translate English day6_hk_e9ec4437:


    nar "Maya suddenly appears in my pitch-dark vision."


translate English day6_hk_91a38660:


    nar "Up until yesterday, we were friends, but waking up to the way things are now has made me take a step back."


translate English day6_hk_a6f23aa0:


    nar "Looking back to the first day we met has made me realize that chance encounter on the train was not as coincidental as I initially thought."


translate English day6_hk_51680d5d:


    nar "It sounds so cliche and yet I feel that we were fated to meet. {w}She was the first priest I met on my way to the capital."


translate English day6_hk_c2fb84e8:


    nar "Everything started from that day."


translate English day6_hk_c59a3f71:


    nar "Working together with her just felt so natural. {w}She's a good girl."


translate English day6_hk_689ccb5a:


    nar "Thanks to how short and quiet Maya is, she has a habit of sneaking up on me without meaning to."


translate English day6_hk_9a3e9b1f:


    nar "Her eyes are always half-closed, and I can never tell if it's from a lack of sleep or just the way she is."


translate English day6_hk_1d2b2c30:


    nar "She's one of the most impressionable people I know, a lovely young girl who, now that I think about it, shares my concern about most things."


translate English day6_hk_6f6a09fc:


    nar "It's been a long week as a member of the Cleanup Department. {w}And it's not over yet."


translate English day6_hk_ea4104fe:


    nar "And yet the more I think about her, the more I realize how short our time was together. {w}And how big of a part she played in my life thus far here in the temple."


translate English day6_hk_797c226f:


    nar "Just remembering her face has opened the floodgates to my memories of everything that's happened since I arrived."


translate English day6_hk_e6d2ada0:


    nar "The piercingly strong scent of detergent, the young buds blooming in the rose garden, the cold desk in the work office... {w}And the angel."


translate English day6_hk_e2837b2a:


    pl "What was that...?"


translate English day6_hk_81a8e5cc:


    nar "As I was reflecting back on everything that's happened to me, a certain face flickered through my mind. {w}Not Maya's."


translate English day6_hk_082054ec:


    nar "Everything bad that's ever happened to me started after running into, not Maya, but *her*."


translate English day6_hk_e4eca25e:


    nar "In the midst of the orange candle flame, burning merrily, I notice a smoldering golden glow."


translate English day6_hk_29a499eb:


    nar "Maybe it's just my imagination, but I find myself growing nauseated. {w}But I'm sure it's just from being in the warehouse for too long."


translate English day6_hk_74b14e4f:


    nar "But trying to get up from my position leaned back against the wall causes the room to spin around me. {w}And I can no longer hear the incessant clanking of the machinery."


translate English day6_hk_8b407c19:


    nar "Did I fall asleep? Come to think of it, my head feels fuzzy and my throat is dry. {w}I don't think it's just from the heat."


translate English day6_hk_0cec89fe:


    nar "I go outside, but the crowded hallways do nothing to dissipate the dreamlike feeling of the world around me."


translate English day6_hk_dc64e69f:


    nar "All that stands out in my mind is the thin, white smoke curling up from the incinerator into the air."


translate English day6_hk_f1b00f77:


    pl "\"*yawn*...\""


translate English day6_hk_7da348ce:


    nar "It's a scene that should leave me sighing in response, but I yawn instead."


translate English day6_hk_46f548aa:


    nar "I wish I knew what time it is, but the midnight sun is so bright I still can't tell whether it's night or day.{w} Good thing I have the day off."


translate English day6_hk_c78bfe31:


    nar "I wish I knew what time it is, but the polar night sky means I have no idea if it's the middle of the night or afternoon. {w}At least I got the day off."


translate English day6_hk_328a6e90:


    nar "Suddenly, I hear the familiar clack of heels on pavement. {w}It's not distinctive to the point where I know exactly who it is, but it's enough that I feel my heart racing reflexively."


translate English day6_hk_5d7b1482:


    nar "I'm disgusted with myself. {w}Mainly because by the time I hear her, she's already right there."


translate English day6_hk_30091a56:


    nar "There's no way I could mistake her for anyone else. {w}There she stands, glowing bright white underneath the cloudy sky, just like the first time we met."


translate English day6_hk_e901d86a:


    hk "\"...\""


translate English day6_hk_d192ed3f:


    nar "When the bishop noticed me, she closed the lid of the container she was holding with a firm snap, {w}looking as if she'd swallowed something wrong."


translate English day6_hk_487e202b:


    nar "She then proceeded to come to an unnatural halt before rapidly approaching me accompanied by the horrifying clack of her heels."


translate English day6_hk_243fb06c:


    hk "You scared me! {w}Brother [na], am I right?"


translate English day6_hk_c6828e0b:


    nar "Her voice, flat and emotionless, doesn't seem to match her words. {w}I guess that bizarre look on her face a moment ago was surprise."


translate English day6_hk_0b6c7fec:


    hk "I assumed we wouldn't be graced by your presence today..."


translate English day6_hk_6c66bfeb:


    hk "It's your day off, is it not? What are you doing here at this time of day?"


translate English day6_hk_3c2fcfe0:


    nar "...This is exactly why I didn't want to see her today."


translate English day6_hk_4a43669e:


    nar "Everything that's happened thus far--my accident yesterday,"


translate English day6_hk_712c7291:


    nar "and the incident this morning--has led to me forming certain opinions about her, {w} though I still haven't made up my mind in full."


translate English day6_hk_4ba11544:


    nar "I was afraid to stand before her while still in a state of vulnerability. {w}I don't hate her. {w}I know she's not a bad person."


translate English day6_hk_2ff2b811:


    nar "But there's no denying that strange things often happen when I'm with her. {w}Incidents that I can't define with the knowledge I have."


translate English day6_hk_8834a12a:


    pl "I had some time to kill so I went for a walk around the temple grounds. {w}That's all. Don't think that I came out here in hopes of seeing you."


translate English day6_hk_dffa0a2b:


    hk "Oh, you came to see me?"


translate English day6_hk_f7d74294:


    pl "Listen when people are talking to you!!!"


translate English day6_hk_f7ac4149:


    hk "Am I wrong? {w}And here I was honestly just thinking to myself how wonderful it would be if I bumped into you."


translate English day6_hk_af19f008:


    pl "Nothing better to do then?"


translate English day6_hk_2c4aa145:


    hk "Brother, we've been sharing secrets over the past few days, haven't we?"


translate English day6_hk_ee2f708f:


    hk "Now then, you're probably wondering how I knew you'd be here of all places, correct?"


translate English day6_hk_4d3ade0d:


    pl "What...?!"


translate English day6_hk_e8411ca5:


    hk "I have a hunch you wanted to burn the image of the Cleanup Department into your memory one more time before making an important decision."


translate English day6_hk_eb1e660c:


    pl "..."


translate English day6_hk_c74edf4e:


    nar "There's no real reason why I came here. {w}I just came, and then I sat down."


translate English day6_hk_a93cb8a3:


    nar "If there's any reason at all, I should be the one to ask... {w}I simply nod my head, unsettled."


translate English day6_hk_fc1da010:


    hk "Heh heh..."


translate English day6_hk_aa007937:


    nar "She smiles at me, shrugging."


translate English day6_hk_335674e1:


    nar "She made me exceedingly self-conscious with her words earlier, though I'm not sure why it affected me that much."


translate English day6_hk_59dbd63a:


    nar "Is it that she places the Cleanup Department's work before herself?"


translate English day6_hk_19116cf0:


    hk "Did you make a decision yet?"


translate English day6_hk_808ab235:


    pl "Didn't you say something about not rushing me?"


translate English day6_hk_203ce3af:


    hk "I ask not as your bishop... {w}but as your friend, Brother [na]. Tell me your secrets."


translate English day6_hk_c7bca095:


    pl "I'm still thinking it over..."


translate English day6_hk_c0b082b2:


    nar "That she is the bishop of the department suddenly becomes crystal clear."


translate English day6_hk_258340bd:


    nar "Why am I only becoming aware of this now? How exactly did I see her before this moment?"


translate English day6_hk_ff30370b:


    nar "She's right, though. We did share quite a very private conversations over the past few days."


translate English day6_hk_fcedb3c1:


    nar "And yet I still don't know anything about this lady called Haku Eckara."


translate English day6_hk_6701211f:


    pl "Actually... I was hoping to talk to you about it. Is that fine?"


translate English day6_hk_9d1287df:


    nar "I ultimately try shaking off this awkward fear I feel toward her while drawing her closer."


translate English day6_hk_eb5aeff8:


    hk "Hmm..."


translate English day6_hk_11c55540:


    nar "She shuts her mouth that never seems at a loss for words and averts her gaze, as if trying to look pained."


translate English day6_hk_ddce0096:


    nar "Even her high-pitched yet soft voice sounds agitated. {w}It's admirable, assuming nothing she's doing is calculated."


translate English day6_hk_839d2029:


    hk "This is a conundrum indeed. The workplace will soon be full of people."


translate English day6_hk_c0ff6093:


    pl "Oh. In that case..."


translate English day6_hk_9faff0b1:


    hk "Shall we continue this in my room?"


translate English day6_hk_168061c0:


    nar "I froze in the midst of the peaceful silence."


translate English day6_hk_a041f8f5:


    nar "I don't think I misheard her. {w}I never felt the existence of the ears on my head as strongly as in that moment."


translate English day6_hk_69a17f85:


    nar "She has this power of making you remember everyday things that tend to slip past your memory with their sheer mundanity."


translate English day6_hk_2e2b31d0:


    nar "And yet once again, just as I touched on briefly before, strange things happen to my body every time I'm with her."


translate English day6_hk_bd9a81a2:


    nar "This is only further proven by the way I stupidly nod my head in response, regardless of my actual inclination."


translate English day6_hk_a62cb6f0:


    nar "On our way back to the dorms, I ask her what time it is."


translate English day6_hk_7c3080c0:


    nar "She tells me it's between noon and dusk and how the priests who went out into town for work should be trickling back soon for dinner."


translate English day6_hk_ffae1725:


    nar "My forgotten thirst and hunger surges through my body in response to her words, but my anxiety quickly dulls both sensations to a faint ache."


translate English day6_hk_d4d10247:


    nar "I've walked down this hallway many times at this point, and yet I find myself gawking distractedly at everything around me, {w}similar to the way I felt when I first arrived."


translate English day6_hk_a84ab800:


    nar "It's the same familiar walls I've passed countless times before. {w}I make sure to keep some distance between the bishop and myself."


translate English day6_hk_372c163c:


    nar "We don't hold hands or walk side-by-side. I'm slightly behind her, letting her lead the way. {w}And yet I still feel anxious."


translate English day6_hk_d163c588:


    nar "We might have exchanged a few words on our way, but I don't remember any of it."


translate English day6_hk_24e11408:


    nar "With the crowds of priests gone, the only sound echoing in my ears is the rhythmic clacking of her heels in the silent corridor."


translate English day6_hk_d2d6c4e0:


    nar "The strings attached to her veil sway side to side with each step as she turns her restless gaze forward."


translate English day6_hk_b8856d0a:


    nar "The bishop is quite tall. {w}If that guy who's always annoyingly around were here, all you'd see would be her hair, tied back and floating above everything else."


translate English day6_hk_fb1a13ae:


    pl "Huh?"


translate English day6_hk_d1ec5a76:


    hk "Hmm?"


translate English day6_hk_6d4c8889:


    nar "We come to a room at the end of the hallway on the first floor and the bishop stops and takes out a key."


translate English day6_hk_765062c5:


    nar "I stop dead in my tracks before grunting inquiringly."


translate English day6_hk_087effa9:


    nar "Having stopped walking as well, she turns to face me, almost as if questioning my reaction."


translate English day6_hk_8acb91c8:


    pl "It's j-just I always assumed your room would be on the topmost floor."


translate English day6_hk_37d27a5e:


    hk "That would surely make it inconvenient any time a priest needed my help."


translate English day6_hk_24b2d7e1:


    pl "So you're saying anyone can just come and pay you a visit?"


translate English day6_hk_262dde37:


    hk "Depending on what they need and how important it is."


translate English day6_hk_64dacd6f:


    pl "But you're always busy with work, right?"


translate English day6_hk_66bf9426:


    hk "Even I have to sleep at night. {w}However, feel free to come to me if you ever need to talk, day or night."


translate English day6_hk_cde2bdba:


    hk "Though I usually go to bed at eight in the evening..."


translate English day6_hk_9e9c8ad1:


    pl "So early..."


translate English day6_hk_7a1d7d01:


    hk "Oh, I've done so ever since I was a young girl."


translate English day6_hk_88a5a257:


    pl "Does anyone actually stop by?"


translate English day6_hk_dfd98344:


    hk "Hmm... Let me think. Brother Securett stopped by to wake me up this morning..."


translate English day6_hk_6b9afc92:


    pl "I see... I didn't realize you're the type to sleep in, Your Excellency."


translate English day6_hk_37995ea3:


    hk "A good night's rest is the secret to maintaining a beautiful physique."


translate English day6_hk_e9cde7cd:


    nar "Moments after I hear the sound of her key turning in the lock, the door opens. {w}I continue glancing around restlessly, just like I've been doing on our way here."


translate English day6_hk_8d57556c:


    nar "I watch as the bishop peels off her knee-high boots before stepping inside the room, and I follow her lead by removing my shoes as well."


translate English day6_hk_ea6dfbe1:


    nar "I'm unsure where to put my shoes, the soles of which are caked in dirt and grime."


translate English day6_hk_76269efd:


    hk "Please, take a seat."


translate English day6_hk_a0cfc084:


    pl "Oh, uh... Sure."


translate English day6_hk_6a02f70e:


    nar "There's no way I can just \"take a seat.\""


translate English day6_hk_4a9825da:


    nar "I'd assumed while on the walk over that her room wouldn't be any different from mine, considering they're both located in the same building."


translate English day6_hk_0f0bb71f:


    nar "But apparently the bishop's room is slightly different compared to the ones assigned to the general population. {w}The furniture is the only part that looks the same."


translate English day6_hk_7b14ece1:


    nar "Seeing as she's a woman, I'd assumed the room would include a floral carpet, rosaries of all shapes and sizes, and would littered with dolls sewn with irregularly colored fabric."


translate English day6_hk_a8007202:


    nar "But instead, it was fairly empty aside from the bare necessities."


translate English day6_hk_b7f4c049:


    nar "She did say she used the space for sleeping only, though the bleak vibe seems unimaginable compared to her usual appearance."


translate English day6_hk_cd6eb84f:


    nar "It's oddly unsettling. The space seems unusually large considering it's only being used to house the minimum amount of furniture necessary for basic human life."


translate English day6_hk_2d5e542c:


    nar "As I sit there by myself in that big room, twiddling my thumbs, I'm suddenly startled by the sound of water coming from the bathroom."


translate English day6_hk_74d4f2ef:


    nar "It wasn't the simple sound of water flowing, but instead that of the faucet being turned on."


translate English day6_hk_5a46f460:


    nar "What is she doing? {w}The cold sweat pouring off my body seems to match the sound of the water running endlessly into the sink."


translate English day6_hk_4e0f6365:


    hk "Do you need to use the bathroom, Brother?"


translate English day6_hk_d46c5525:


    pl "Me? {w}Uh... I'm fine. Why do you ask?"


translate English day6_hk_5e925a42:


    hk "I always wash my hands whenever I return to my room."


translate English day6_hk_642fb55a:


    pl "Oh, I see..."


translate English day6_hk_3e1570a1:


    nar "I look up to see her drying her hands, wiping the water droplets from her skin. {w}I feel like my over-heated thoughts are starting to cool down."


translate English day6_hk_5d766dc5:


    pl "Seems like a huge hassle to wash your hands with sleeves that long."


translate English day6_hk_701fd2da:


    hk "Yes... There's truth to that. But I feel that it's important to hide one's hands until they're needed for something important. {w}Cleanliness and purity is a virtue."


translate English day6_hk_10175d1b:


    pl "Haha..."


translate English day6_hk_6b792266:


    hk "Is there anything I can get for you?"


translate English day6_hk_aeee5b17:


    pl "Mm... Well, a glass of water would be nice."


translate English day6_hk_ec4fe8ce:


    hk "Of course."


translate English day6_hk_90c930dd:


    nar "I hear the sound of the tap turning back on again and realize I'm way too tense."


translate English day6_hk_221e2c09:


    nar "Despite the awkwardness I'm feeling sitting here,"


translate English day6_hk_f5ba23ec:


    nar "there's really no reason why I should be feeling this uncomfortable and impatient."


translate English day6_hk_44c7535f:


    nar "I pick up a hint of sour lemon in the warm water she hands me."


translate English day6_hk_56674138:


    nar "It's only after gulping down two cups of water that my cold sweat finally evaporated."


translate English day6_hk_ddac432b:


    hk "My, my... Someone's thirsty."


translate English day6_hk_989363d7:


    pl "My throat's been really dry lately, for some reason. I'm assuming it has to do with the poor air quality in the workplace."


translate English day6_hk_a67aca9f:


    hk "Are you sure it's not out of discomfort?"


translate English day6_hk_53f89df5:


    pl "Mmm... Well, I'm sure that has something to do with it. This room does seem pretty big for one person."


translate English day6_hk_73bac48f:


    hk "I have a feeling it's bigger than the other rooms. There's a bathtub, too, you know."


translate English day6_hk_485149dc:


    pl "Seriously? That's unfair. I'd love not to be forced to use the communal showers..."


translate English day6_hk_dda060a8:


    pl "I was surprised at how big it was, and yet surprisingly bare at the same time. {w}The white walls and floors makes them feel more barren than anything..."


translate English day6_hk_6c8da27b:


    hk "As I said before, I'm always here if any of my priests ever need me."


translate English day6_hk_7c4397fe:


    pl "What exactly are you getting at?"


translate English day6_hk_1376b21d:


    hk "Well... When you first imagined what my room might look like, Brother [na], how exactly did you picture it? {w}Something like this?"


translate English day6_hk_c9e5b2e6:


    pl "Well, no. I figured there would be a carpet at least, perhaps a painting made by a famous artist from the capital, a doll as big as a house... That kind of stuff."


translate English day6_hk_4f5ef436:


    hk "Wow... All of that sounds good to me  Charming..."


translate English day6_hk_b9e7ebb7:


    pl "But you don't have any of that."


translate English day6_hk_5c6e4002:


    hk "A room is nothing more than a living space. And it is in that space that the owner of said room dwells."


translate English day6_hk_c61c5193:


    hk "By taking that person's interests into consideration and filling the space with all manner of things they enjoy, {w}you create a seamless space that's very personal."


translate English day6_hk_8a61e9ac:


    hk "So seamless that no one else may enter. {w}It's hard for others to become comfortable in a space so full of someone else's soul, so filled with their very spirit."


translate English day6_hk_5323fb56:


    pl "On the other hand, this place feels exactly the opposite."


translate English day6_hk_2af5830d:


    hk "Heh... And yet if you look closer, you'll see I have everything I need."


translate English day6_hk_6ea06d54:


    hk "I spend every night here, I pray, I make sure my appearance is presentable and I write in my diary at that very desk."


translate English day6_hk_edd9f562:


    pl "That's quite a classy hobby."


translate English day6_hk_a0821f20:


    hk "One that helps keep my thoughts in order and my soul in check."


translate English day6_hk_81f590b0:


    nar "As we continue talking, I begin spotting items in the room I'd been too nervous to notice when I first came inside."


translate English day6_hk_34f531f5:


    nar "There's a diary-like notebook on her desk, just like she said, along with a candle. {w}Meanwhile, I notice several objects scattered about her dresser, which is fixed with a mirror."


translate English day6_hk_deee80a7:


    nar "They're all evidence that this room belongs to a woman."


translate English day6_hk_9db611b4:


    hk "Now then... What's on your mind? How can I help you, Brother?"


translate English day6_hk_48b0cbdb:


    nar "I'm sure she can easily guess what's on my mind, but she's asking me anyway."


translate English day6_hk_48e7893d:


    nar "She sits down on the side of her bed as she speaks, and I notice the sheets are slightly rumpled. {w}I get a flash of how she must look like waking up every morning."


translate English day6_hk_d9ca23ff:


    nar "If I think about it too much, I'll start to get nervous. {w}I force myself to gulp down the melted ice cube in hopes of distracting myself."


translate English day6_hk_eff7b0a3:


    nar "Now, how much of what's going on should I tell her?"


translate English day6_hk_3ba6d8ff:


    pl "It's not that I necessarily want to stay in the Cleanup Department, nor do I not want to join the Magic Department. I don't think so, at least. {w}It's just that..."


translate English day6_hk_3c156559:


    hk "You're still conflicted. {w}Is that about right?"


translate English day6_hk_e7729b44:


    pl "It's not like you to be the one to finish another's thoughts."


translate English day6_hk_b9f9a0a7:


    hk "To be fair, you are really taking your time formulating your thoughts."


translate English day6_hk_247aaf7c:


    pl "I'm trying to make sure the words I use are the right ones, just like you do so often."


translate English day6_hk_e9d6e318:


    nar "She has a look on her face of someone who's ready to lend an ear and give advice..."


translate English day6_hk_bb734716:


    hk "Do you have any lingering doubts?"


translate English day6_hk_5c9927c1:


    pl "Quite a few, in fact."


translate English day6_hk_218a83f9:


    pl "I can't say I've gotten along well with the other folks in the Cleanup Department, but that I have no friends there would be an outright lie."


translate English day6_hk_98153915:


    hk "Is there anyone in particular that you've grown close to?"


translate English day6_hk_a772c3fd:


    pl "That's quite a leading question, Your Excellency."


translate English day6_hk_c78a194b:


    hk "That question came from genuine curiosity, I promise."


translate English day6_hk_03655a9c:


    pl "Well... Yes, actually. {w}Though I'm still not exactly sure why that matters to me."


translate English day6_hk_1001333e:


    pl "I'm simply changing departments, not leaving the temple. {w}And though I worry about her, I'm not the only person who can look out for Maya."


translate English day6_hk_8d32fed8:


    hk "Are you okay with the change, Brother [na]?"


translate English day6_hk_eb4b8dc8:


    pl "Me? I'll certainly miss seeing the people in my life who I've grown familiar with, {w}but I'm sure I'll still get to see them, and we'll still remain friends, right?"


translate English day6_hk_de0b48f7:


    pl "Plus, I can always make new friends in the Magic Department..."


translate English day6_hk_c6a985ad:


    hk "Correct."


translate English day6_hk_c21a6344:


    pl "I've always been a fast learner. That I started off on such a bad foot in the Cleanup Department was a fluke."


translate English day6_hk_1263e9b0:


    hk "Did you just read my mind?"


translate English day6_hk_045eca8d:


    pl "I'd prefer if you didn't think way that about me!"


translate English day6_hk_d83f5a3b:


    hk "You might be okay with the change, Brother [na], but there's no mistake that your friends will miss you."


translate English day6_hk_08f25edd:


    pl "Which is another difficult problem... But it's not like I want my friends to be sad because of me."


translate English day6_hk_10c1abcf:


    hk "Why do you feel that way?"


translate English day6_hk_5115218b:


    pl "Without diving too deep into the situation, I feel like I never really had a choice in the matter."


translate English day6_hk_05cf4406:


    pl "I never had any intention of refusing your request, though if I did, all your problems would be solved in one way or another."


translate English day6_hk_96b1bc9f:


    hk "I feel as if I've been dumped into an absurd situation."


translate English day6_hk_989e3a40:


    pl "And I think you've shared a similar experience. {w}When you were first offered the position of bishop in the Cleanup Department, how did you feel?"


translate English day6_hk_61c78226:


    hk "I accepted it as an honor, akin to a gift from Heaven itself. {w}Though I understand where you're coming from..."


translate English day6_hk_332f793d:


    hk "There's no mistaking my dreamy state of mind at the time, but regardless, there was no possibility of me turning down their offer."


translate English day6_hk_d7aa6fec:


    hk "Any refusal on my part would have been deemed an inexcusable action, akin to strangling myself."


translate English day6_hk_186e51d1:


    pl "Th-That's just a metaphor, right?"


translate English day6_hk_0efe5b38:


    hk "Yes, of course! {w}Though at the time, I had absolutely no intention of saying no to taking on the role of bishop."


translate English day6_hk_ae095fb5:


    hk "So I never agonized over my decision, not even for one second."


translate English day6_hk_901138ec:


    pl "Don't get me wrong, I don't plan on looking a gift horse in the mouth."


translate English day6_hk_e4c3ae4a:


    hk "But you feel a sense of... rejection almost?"


translate English day6_hk_ca7e4951:


    pl "It's not a transfer that I've earned on my own merit. {w}It doesn't make me feel good. Especially since the folks there have high hopes for my worth and capabilities."


translate English day6_hk_7159b13c:


    pl "That is a heavy burden to bear."


translate English day6_hk_7cedf844:


    hk "Are you afraid of discovering your own limitations?"


translate English day6_hk_bbd924f4:


    pl "I'm afraid those limitations will end up burdening others."


translate English day6_hk_0c95ee3c:


    hk "Their high expectations aren't baseless, you know. They truly believe in what you can do..."


translate English day6_hk_1d4b31fd:


    pl "It's not something I can overcome with hard work or luck. It's definitely a me problem."


translate English day6_hk_7f0f98a8:


    pl "Determination... talent... That kind of thing, you know. {w}At the very least, it's an honor that I can't turn down, similar to your acceptance of your position as bishop."


translate English day6_hk_de5bd8a8:


    pl "I'm sure it's due to my own lack of faith. I'm well aware."


translate English day6_hk_4963c575:


    nar "The bishop falls silent at that. {w}Though I'm sure most folks would've been left speechless in her position."


translate English day6_hk_88767898:


    nar "I already know what she's going to say when she opens her mouth again. {w}Cliched words of encouragement, thoughts and prayers on my behalf, or a lecture..."


translate English day6_hk_1c9e9b1c:


    hkn "Bishop Erzsebet of the Magic Department is a very wise man. {w}I'm sure there must be a reason why he chose you to join them."


translate English day6_hk_8910fdaf:


    hkn "God is the same way. {w}Those chosen by him must live up to certain expectations, thus proving his confidence in their ability to do so."


translate English day6_hk_1005834f:


    hkn "Your talents are going to waste in the underworld, Brother [na]. {w}You were chosen for bigger and better things."


translate English day6_hk_c7db01ee:


    pl "...?"


translate English day6_hk_ca86646c:


    hkn "That they hope you can accomplish something new with your ability and determination"


translate English day6_hk_ac27e733:


    hkn "should be seen as a mark of pride."


translate English day6_hk_c51784bd:


    hkn "I won't pretend to know exactly what the bishop of the Magic Department is thinking..."


translate English day6_hk_7beac163:


    hkn "though I'm sure they have the power to do whatever they want without anyone else's help. {w}Despite your existence in the underworld,"


translate English day6_hk_66241716:


    hkn "you were chosen, meaning I have confidence that you'll be accomplish whatever role is given to you."


translate English day6_hk_7929140e:


    pl "So what you're saying is that I'm nothing more than a pawn in a chess game too big for me to perceive?"


translate English day6_hk_7c2d6784:


    hk "Hmm... {w}Well... that's certainly a possibility."


translate English day6_hk_bf313eb1:


    pl "The bishop of the Magic Department is one thing, but to bring God into this... Well, it's not something I expected to hear coming your mouth."


translate English day6_hk_aca28dc4:


    hk "And why is that? {w}After all, what are we but pawns on God's larger than life chessboard, acting out His will?"


translate English day6_hk_e63f137b:


    hk "And we fulfill our destinies as a show of thanks to God for gracing each of us with life as we weave our way through the world."


translate English day6_hk_035a85d9:


    hk "It's not necessarily a bad thing. And it's not like the Cleanup Department is any different."


translate English day6_hk_22f2292d:


    pl "Can you still be satisfied knowing that?"


translate English day6_hk_fd1221da:


    hk "Not only was a given a part to play, but I'm able to help others simply by doing my job."


translate English day6_hk_2d8051bf:


    pl "Thanks for talking with me about all this... but it looks like we're gonna have to agree to disagree."


translate English day6_hk_ee9a0de0:


    hk "Is it due to your lack of faith, Brother?"


translate English day6_hk_cf26fcb3:


    pl "To be fair, most of what you have to say is pretty out there."


translate English day6_hk_08ae140a:


    hk "You find me so strange?"


translate English day6_hk_e1269283:


    pl "Is that bad?"


translate English day6_hk_b5fef447:


    hk "Not necessarily. It seems rather fitting, actually."


translate English day6_hk_ebc6d3cd:


    pl "Maybe I'm the crazy one! Honestly, I've been wondering if I've lost my damn mind ever since I got here."


translate English day6_hk_788f8894:


    pl "And honestly, talking with you only seems to make it worse, Haku."


translate English day6_hk_06930c27:


    hk "Heh heh heh... Hee hee..."


translate English day6_hk_cf83adfc:


    pl "Not again. What did I say this time?"


translate English day6_hk_87667101:


    hk "It just amuses me the way you place emphasize on the first part of my name over the second..."


translate English day6_hk_d0be2f4c:


    pl "Look... Don't make fun of other people's accents!"


translate English day6_hk_4b56bc95:


    pl "I come across my fair share of weird names here in the capital, but yours seriously takes the cake."


translate English day6_hk_3e72dc86:


    hk "I love when folks call me by my name. {w}Your accent is so fascinating, Brother [na]. It's almost like listening to music..."


translate English day6_hk_5fff4507:


    pl "The way she bursts into laughter, cry without warning, or suddenly start sulking over seemingly nothing... {w}I never get tired of watching her."


translate English day6_hk_6209615b:


    hk "I'm like a blank sheet of paper, filled with the colorful words I hear from the brothers and sisters, including yourself, that I pass by every day."


translate English day6_hk_3648bc09:


    pl "Is that a reference to the Pestis wiping your memories clean?"


translate English day6_hk_762c4ab7:


    hk "That has something to do with it, but also every morning when I wake up, I feel like I'm reborn anew..."


translate English day6_hk_f2d08e59:


    hk "I feel as if there's a hole, not in my head but somewhere in my very existence..."


translate English day6_hk_55114e85:


    hk "You've allowed to fall in love with the world in a brand new way, and for that I'm grateful."


translate English day6_hk_6226d53a:


    pl "You're a very magnanimous person, in a variety of ways..."


translate English day6_hk_66fce9ce:


    hk "I'm honored to hear you say that."


translate English day6_hk_54d183cb:


    pl "How can you live with such a liberal mindset?"


translate English day6_hk_2c3aa2cd:


    hk "I'm happy to explain, though I'm not sure how helpful it'll be..."


translate English day6_hk_941ff6c8:


    hk "Never once has it ever crossed my mind that I must somehow try and live up to someone else's expectations of me."


translate English day6_hk_cda940aa:


    hk "I guess I trust in my ability to do so without extra effort."


translate English day6_hk_f7712f88:


    pl "Aren't you contradicting yourself?"


translate English day6_hk_055d69ee:


    hk "Of course--though I've never compared myself to anyone else."


translate English day6_hk_fd1c854c:


    hk "I simply focusing on carrying out the matters entrusted in my care."


translate English day6_hk_23412f2b:


    hk "I don't ever want you to feel that your trust for me has been misplaced... {w}Which is why I'm always happy to admit when I don't remember something."


translate English day6_hk_63613a5c:


    pl "Ha! I kind of get it. I was pretty flustered myself on my first day here."


translate English day6_hk_c5258ce2:


    hk "Most folks, when they first start out, tend to only ask about those who've already passed on, though their numbers have dwindled lately."


translate English day6_hk_e465a816:


    pl "Hold on. What do you mean?"


translate English day6_hk_84ace47a:


    hk "Huh? {w}I'm sorry, I didn't explain myself well enough. {w}I didn't mean to startle you."


translate English day6_hk_283325ca:


    hk "I'm one of those who have returned, to be more precise."


translate English day6_hk_d821bd01:


    pl "You're not making any sense."


translate English day6_hk_3d54659a:


    hk "My absence of memories is proof that my very essence is gone, that unique personality I once possessed is no more."


translate English day6_hk_f9ccb410:


    hk "According to stories I've heard, I used to be quite stubborn and out of control, like an unbridled mare."


translate English day6_hk_665d25cf:


    hk "When they talk about me, it sounds like they're speaking of a stranger."


translate English day6_hk_42bc3c14:


    hk "The way that I am now, it's impossible for me to regain the personality of that person I once was."


translate English day6_hk_9aaecdd7:


    hk "I exist here, in this form now, and though I'm in no danger of disappearing... {w}for all intents and purposes, I am dead."


translate English day6_hk_50494a69:


    hk "So I use the phrase \"to return\" in respect of those who are like me."


translate English day6_hk_9b9991cf:


    pl "I've found it difficult to follow most of what you say, but this time, you've completely lost me."


translate English day6_hk_2dc92cac:


    pl "Once you've become a shell of your former self, with no memories of who you once were, {w}it makes things awkward when you meet people you once knew."


translate English day6_hk_0b0a4530:


    hk "But I'm not saying that past version of myself never existed."


translate English day6_hk_b617cf2a:


    hk "I just can't remember... {w}I'm sure you know how I feel to some degree."


translate English day6_hk_f19e91ef:


    hk "It's like when someone who's known you since you were a baby tells you stories about things you did as a child..."


translate English day6_hk_b8cc60e1:


    pl "Is it really necessary to refer to yourself as dead?"


translate English day6_hk_bf5ac25f:


    hk "It's nothing more than a state of mind."


translate English day6_hk_38e62673:


    hk "As a woman, I too fear growing old, but that fear doesn't make me yearn for a second chance at adolescence."


translate English day6_hk_4e0867cd:


    hk "My brush with death makes me feel reborn in a way."


translate English day6_hk_fc829b8d:


    hk "By re-experiencing that newness of life similar to when I was born, I can live as a young girl forever."


translate English day6_hk_9e900bba:


    hk "Though \"purification\" might be more fitting in this situation than \"death\"..."


translate English day6_hk_46466507:


    pl "Purification..."


translate English day6_hk_70bb57e0:


    nar "The way she uses the word \"death\" is similar to how she described an immortal soul that one time."


translate English day6_hk_f22bd5dc:


    nar "Moreover, philosophy by its very nature is an intricate and fragile construct,"


translate English day6_hk_9edd96ac:


    nar "like miniature animals tottering over one's fingers, easily crushed with the slightest amount of force."


translate English day6_hk_019667f9:


    nar "But I'm too far gone to be able to waste time with a more discreet approach."


translate English day6_hk_9b429be3:


    pl "So basically, it's only through your continual shifting of blame onto others that you're able to retain this sense of virtuosity."


translate English day6_hk_dce3b778:


    pl "Also, I'm not sure if feeling young at heart with a soul purged of depravity is worth anything if your body continues to age."


translate English day6_hk_4626a1dd:


    hk "A woman unfamiliar with poetry has no hope of being beautiful."


translate English day6_hk_bd8fad8e:


    hk "I have that beauty, and if I may interject, the only one talking about shifting blame"


translate English day6_hk_4e85d319:


    hk "in order to cleanse one's soul is YOU."


translate English day6_hk_ddc0d730:


    pl "That's rich, coming from you, Haku, {w}especially after yesterday."


translate English day6_hk_cc77343b:


    hk "Ah..."


translate English day6_hk_a09b1378:


    nar "The finger she used to poke me in the chest withdraws."

translate English day6_hk_da56bda3:


    nar "There was no warmth in that single digit, even through the glove. It felt as hard as a rock."


translate English day6_hk_620958f2:


    nar "And that smile I'm used to seeing on her face is back."


translate English day6_hk_823f9494:


    nar "Would I sound like I lost my damn mind if I said that smile tended to mock my unpopular opinion almost seems to glow with benevolence?"


translate English day6_hk_0007eaf9:


    nar "Regardless, I don't doubt my own eyes."


translate English day6_hk_bc69d03f:


    nar "If God creates humans for the sole purpose of carrying out his will in the form of some greater divine purpose,"


translate English day6_hk_39dd67c6:


    nar "then she is the embodiment of that vessel."


translate English day6_hk_cf09e507:


    nar "A being more pure and delicate than anyone in the world. {w}Which is why she's empty and feels unfulfilled no matter what she does."


translate English day6_hk_b8e3f6ab:


    pl "There's one thing I want to ask you... You like the cardinal, don't you? {w}What more could you possibly want?"


translate English day6_hk_9840a830:


    hk "I want everything. {w}And yet even if I got it, I still wouldn't be satisfied."


translate English day6_hk_48438ad4:


    hk "It's similar to having graciously accepted your blessing and feeling completely unchanged by it."


translate English day6_hk_aa82f597:


    pl "I'm sure we were just missing something. Maybe we weren't prepared. {w}Or like making sure both my arms were in their rightful positions."


translate English day6_hk_024f1436:


    hk "Would it have worked better with a bit more blood?"


translate English day6_hk_ff21c133:


    pl "No need to go that far... Don't you usually say a prayer or partake in some kind of ritual? {w}Not like I'm the type of guy to stand on ceremony.."


translate English day6_hk_dc3e26bf:


    hk "It's my fault for being distracted."


translate English day6_hk_fb518740:


    hk "Heh heh... I think it's pretty cute to worry about others whilst being worshipped."


translate English day6_hk_3030810f:


    pl "Most people don't tend to like those who see their own flaws as cute."


translate English day6_hk_b7724dc6:


    hk "You don't hate me, though, right?"


translate English day6_hk_9694e4ee:


    pl "Let me ask one more question. What exactly do you wish your relationship with the cardinal was exactly?"


translate English day6_hk_6e7c395e:


    hk "I always wanted to become my father's woman. {w}To have a lifelong, heartfelt, and absolute connection with him."


translate English day6_hk_253a6bf5:


    hk "Or in terms you might understand, I wanted to have sex with him."


translate English day6_hk_26727274:


    pl "Despite your vows?"


translate English day6_hk_5b9cdb5a:


    hk "It is precisely because of my vows that I wanted him! You see, the thing is..."


translate English day6_hk_21707d8c:


    hk "One cannot truly give oneself to god without first accepting death."


translate English day6_hk_d64a4a47:


    hk "Which is why we give our souls to God but our bodies, the vessels of God's will, to our parents."


translate English day6_hk_4e872b72:


    pl "I thought you were adopted."


translate English day6_hk_feeeba5c:


    hk "Which furthers the need to forge a relationship. {w}In doing so, we can be truly united as a family. That is the nature of the Sacrament."


translate English day6_hk_6d087a67:


    hk "It's a holy ritual that celebrates the union of immature suffering and true love through the shedding of the blood of the Holy Virgin."


translate English day6_hk_8c603cc6:


    pl "Is that what you go around telling people?"


translate English day6_hk_090545aa:


    hk "Of course not... But I feel free to confess this kind of thing to you since I know it won't affect your view of me."


translate English day6_hk_eb1e660c_1:


    pl "..."


translate English day6_hk_bdc1a61f:


    nar "I'm frustrated that her egotistical mouth is still saying nothing but the truth. {w}It's clear she thinks only of herself."


translate English day6_hk_2c88bf92:


    nar "My unexploded rage flows through my veins to every corner of my body before subsiding into sadness."


translate English day6_hk_ad81db5f:


    nar "She must have sensed as much looking at me."


translate English day6_hk_6e862b5d:


    pl "I'm not good enough, am I?"


translate English day6_hk_c82635d0:


    nar "In the end, I'm left muttering excuses. Nothing I'm saying makes any sense. {w}I hang my head in shame."


translate English day6_hk_753d623d:


    nar "Like a condemned man who can do nothing but accept his own rapidly approaching death, {w}I prostrate myself on the ground."


translate English day6_hk_b61755b4:


    nar "She doesn't seem bothered in the slightest, as if used to this kind of reaction."


translate English day6_hk_a42a4631:


    nar "She knows full well that she was born to be praised and worshipped."


translate English day6_hk_f1ef37f1:


    hk "I have no intention of embracing such basic things like love and faith."


translate English day6_hk_d999d025:


    hk "I imagined how it might be only once. {w}Not just a man, but my father, the Absolute being who gave life to me..."


translate English day6_hk_d4cf6dcc:


    hk "My real family... {w}What we lust over, what we yearn for... The more we speak of it, the more fleeting and ephemeral it grows."


translate English day6_hk_bbdc4d3b:


    pl "You'll always be hungry if you're constantly wanting more."


translate English day6_hk_f20e2d97:


    hk "That is sadly true..."


translate English day6_hk_36658a26:


    hk "I cannot deny my own feelings of love. Sometimes..."


translate English day6_hk_2e7c4575:


    hk "I have idly wondered if I was born solely for this purpose."


translate English day6_hk_cb2cb966:


    hk "From the day of my first menstruation... my blood has flowed from my body solely for the sake of my father,"


translate English day6_hk_fad81392:


    hk "and I hunger to be his someday, body and soul."


translate English day6_hk_39ae2248:


    nar "Frankly, I can't concentrate on what she's saying anymore."


translate English day6_hk_d33c1cc1:


    nar "But there's no way I'm forgetting that riveting love story of hers, that sublime mouth filling my ears with an incestuous tale that's been building for years..."


translate English day6_hk_68314b09:


    hk "Do you know of a custom amongst folks here in the capital where a woman feeds her own menstrual blood to the man she loves?"


translate English day6_hk_ea9cc320:


    hk "Everyone laughs it off as nothing more than a childish superstition, except for me."


translate English day6_hk_13bde8d9:


    hk "Once a woman belongs to someone, their blood flow abruptly stops."


translate English day6_hk_2a3ba2b2:


    hk "The rest of us are left to suffer the indignation of failure, to stopper the hatred that flows down our legs, {w}and learn from our mistakes so the next month might be better."


translate English day6_hk_c047a363:


    hk "That we might find a wonderful and true love of our own."


translate English day6_hk_f69f944e:


    pl "That's not love, just lust."


translate English day6_hk_e7b602bb:


    hk "Love is nothing but lust, after all... Though it's forbidden to harbor such desires in one's heart."


translate English day6_hk_58b42dd2:


    hk "I'm surprised you're asking these kinds of questions after having made up your mind."


translate English day6_hk_e43018fa:


    hk "It's not long before you'll leave my flock, beloved Brother."


translate English day6_hk_b3de7cde:


    nar "She stretches one arm toward me in a comforting embrace. {w}Meanwhile, I can hear alarm bells going off in my head."


translate English day6_hk_bd41e84e:


    nar "I've been told that everyone has their own unique body smell, but I don't detect any kind of scent from her at all."


translate English day6_hk_333deab2:


    nar "But that doesn't mean it's not there. More like I've probably grown used to it."


translate English day6_hk_ccf99dbe:


    nar "It's a musky scent, cut by perfumes and soap, reminiscent of the work room."


translate English day6_hk_1a13653a:


    nar "The bitter stench of smoke on her clothes calms my racing heart."


translate English day6_hk_7f28b0d2:


    pl "Mm..."


translate English day6_hk_96ddff7d:


    nar "At some point, the sound of a heartbeat mixed with steady breathing has grown louder and clearer. {w}I realize it's coming from me."


translate English day6_hk_64ae6bc6:


    nar "She has the ability to draw out potential from others because she is a blank slate."


translate English day6_hk_56833d46:


    nar "In her presence, lies and bluffs, moderation and cardinal principals fall to the wayside."


translate English day6_hk_c75ef291:


    nar "}She embodies the feelings I've struggled with since my bizarre accident."


translate English day6_hk_48751ffd:


    nar "As I focus on my breathing, my face is close enough to her neck that I can see several fine hairs."


translate English day6_hk_3359554a:


    nar "I hear a quiet chuckle next to me, tickling my ear, but it stops as soon as it starts."


translate English day6_hk_d16ae4ff:


    nar "And then, it's silent."


translate English day6_hk_2321d456:


    nar "She watches silently as the buttons on her shirt are unbuttoned, first one and then the next. {w}The only sound is the clambering in my own head."


translate English day6_hk_4665beb0:


    nar "The room is deathly quiet, except for one brief moment when the silence is broken."


translate English day6_hk_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


