translate English day6_hk_226cde9a:


    nar "Before I lose consciousness, I find myself looking deep into someone else's eyes."


translate English day6_hk_616e435b:


    nar "There's a horrifically crude sensation, as if my heart has somehow moved into my brain."


translate English day6_hk_c679f8a8:


    nar "It's followed by a slight ringing in my ears as the tension drains from my body."


translate English day6_hk_afad32b4:


