translate English day6_hk_392477e1:


    nar "I groan in pain when I suddenly feel a faintly familiar sensation."


translate English day6_hk_d5c2f865:


    nar "The feeling of a gentle yet clumsy hand brushing my bangs from my sweaty forehead. {w}I slowly open my eyes once more. {w}The person who's with me has to be..."


