    my "You don't remember...?"


translate English day6_hk_b791fcb7:


    nar "Hearing her words, I try to recollect the events that led to this moment, but my memories are hazy. What did I do? What did I say? What did I hear?"


translate English day6_hk_28590b88:


    nar "It's like the memories from my recent past are simply gone, never to be retrieved."


translate English day6_hk_e3e194e8:


    nar "But the feelings from those moments remain vividly clear, like something from a lucid dream."


translate English day6_hk_3831035c:


    nar "A dream...? {w}Maybe it really was just a dream."


translate English day6_hk_e8ff5362:


    nar "It's a hypothetical idea, but perhaps the reason why I can't stop thinking about it is because I know it'll never happen again."


translate English day6_hk_436d17bd:


    nar "She exists theoretically."


translate English day6_hk_3b988496:


    nar "Making it pointless to try and extract her existence from distant memories, no matter how much I wish I could see her again."


translate English day6_hk_0f5a0336:


    nar "Haku only existed in that moment because I thought of her and talked to her."


translate English day6_hk_dd8b597a:


    nar "But that version of her has long since vanished from my mind. {w}And if she somehow still exists, it's only as an empty shell."


translate English day6_hk_8b472d39:


    nar "Because she's not innocent. {w}She's built more intricately than anyone else in the temple, seemingly complete the way she is."


translate English day6_hk_a44d8347:


    nar "To share her metaphor, it's like she's dead."


translate English day6_hk_741723ab:


    my "You weren't in the cafeteria, so I came looking for you... If you don't know why you're here, [na2], I certainly don't."


translate English day6_hk_c6d46a75:


    pl "That makes sense."


translate English day6_hk_b0f13e0e:


    nar "I appreciate that she's defined things in that way. {w}But it's frustrating at the same time."


translate English day6_hk_54f6bd48:


    nar "The only thing I ultimately discovered was how she is now, because I didn't exist in her past life."


translate English day6_hk_f6f24cc7:


    nar "I should have focused on simply being with her in the present instead of trying to uncover secrets from her past."


translate English day6_hk_f7bcaac0:


    nar "But there's no point losing sleep over what might have been. {w}It's something I've learned quite well over the past few days spent with her."


translate English day6_hk_d83aa143:


    nar "And though I'm not really sure what's going on..."


translate English day6_hk_78786857:


    pl "Thanks for helping me, Maya. {w}In fact, you always seem to be helping me out."


translate English day6_hk_a6a97506:


    my "That's my line... Are you hungry?"


translate English day6_hk_f73b4682:


    pl "Mm, not really."


translate English day6_hk_07401daf:


    nar "I like mingling with others. {w}And spending time with her fulfills that desire in me."


translate English day6_hk_8f5b0349:


    nar "Those who endlessly think, investigate, and draw conclusions from their observations will never flourish, no matter how hard they try."


translate English day6_hk_a3f48e8a:


    nar "I enjoy thinking about her. {w}Maybe I'm in love with her?"


translate English day6_hk_e2c06b11:


    nar "Or perhaps, subconsciously, I've come to worship her against my better judgment."


